## API Testing Scenarios

### Scenario 1

GIVEN the user is trying to access the Diary App
WHEN they enter existing credentials to the email and password fields
THEN they are able to obtain a valid token
AND log in & view the home page

### Scenario 2 (GET Validation Scenario)

GIVEN the user is logged in
WHEN they are in the home page
THEN they are able to see any and all of their expected posts shown

### Scenario 3 (POST Validation Scenario)

GIVEN the user is logged in
WHEN they are in the home page and post an entry
THEN they are able to verify such an entry was created
AND are able to access it by clicking on it(using GET to validate the POST)
